        <p class="TableTextEmphasis">mc-conditions</p>
        <p class="TableText">Normally you would apply a condition to a piece of content or a file. This property lets you also set conditions on styles, which you can then apply to content. This is simply another alternative and might be more efficient for some authors. You might even find that you use both methods in your projects. </p>
